# Infiniware Simple License
Version 1.0 // 2026

This license is designed to encourage individual use and innovation while protecting the integrity of the **Infiniware** ecosystem. It is a simple, human-readable agreement that prioritizes honesty and fair play.

Short version: Be honest, stay human, and don't steal the brand identity.

---

### 1. Grant of Use
Infiniware grants you a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use, run, and interact with our provided software for any personal or professional purpose, provided that you comply with the brand usage terms.

### 2. Redistribution & Cloning
You may NOT repackage, white-label, or redistribute Infiniware software as a standalone product or as part of another bundle without significant modification or express written consent. Simple cloning of the UI/layout for competitive purposes is prohibited.

### 3. Intellectual Property & Attribution
All logos, design systems, and brand assets are intellectual property of Infiniware. If you utilize significant structural pieces of our public code in your own project, a visible attribution (e.g., "Inspired by Infiniware") is required.

### 4. Disclaimer of Warranty
The software is provided "as is," without any warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any damages or data issues arising from the interaction with our tools.

